  <text>
    <body><div type="letter">
      <p>Weddy Night</p>
      <p>Dearest W. I send the Cab, because was found too dangerous for even the Groom to ride; &amp; I therefore want to keep the phaeton tomorrow for the children to go out in, &amp; that I may accompany them on horseback; for today I have not rode.--</p>
      <p>Avis Phoenix</p>
    </div></body>
